{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "There was no difference between \"AI\" and \"Human + AI\" advice, t < 1.",
    "Empathy ratings were significantly higher for \"Human\" advice compared to \"AI\", b = 0.13, t(1227.00) = 2.98, p =.003, and \"Human + AI\" advice, b = 0.17, t(1227.00) = 4.13, p <.001.",
    "Along the same lines, \"Human\" advice was rated as significantly more reliable than \"AI\" advice, b = 0.22, t(1227.00) = 6.06, p <.001, and \"Human + AI\" advice, b = 0.24, t(1227.00) = 6.64, p <.001.",
    "However, perceived comprehensibility did neither differ significantly between \"Human\" and \"AI\" advice, b = 0.01, t < 1, nor between \"Human\" and \"Human + AI\" advice, b = 0.03, t < 1.",
    "Finally, the willingness to follow \"Human\" advice was significantly higher compared to \"AI\" advice, b = 0.18, t(1227.00) = 4.58, p <.001, and \"Human + AI\" advice, b = 0.18, t(1227.00) = 4.58, p <.001."
  ],
